data.description: Feast your eyes upon this classic 4 bedroom dream home in River Ridge. Restored after Ida, this house received a new roof, new vinyl wood flooring, 2 new A/C units and a new hot water heater. Now it's just waiting for it's new owner. In addition to all it's renovations, this house boast a large living area with a gas brick fireplace, a wall of built-in shelving and wall of windows with a glass door leading to the back patio. Adjacent to the living area is a large formal dining room and an office/flex room. The kitchen includes an office nook and access to the separate laundry room, garage and hall bath. The garage is outfitted with tons of shelving, can fit two vehicles and has electric garage door. On the other side of the house, the private primary bedroom has a large attached bathroom with a newly renovated walk-in shower and a large walk-in closet. Each of the closets in the house are furnished with custom shelving. The house comes with a natural gas generator that powers the bedroom half of the house. The front and backyards are shaded by two gorgeous, mature oak trees and a beautiful magnolia tree. The curved driveway provides extra parking space and privacy. You really have to see this one in person.
